8	--
9	-- Description:
10	-- -------------------------------------
11	--		This packages describes common primitives like flip flops and multiplexers
12	--		as a function to use them as one-liners.
13	--
14	--	ATTENSION:
15	--		The parameter 'constant INIT' of some functions is actually the reset
16	--		value, not the initial value after device programming (e.g. for FPGAs),
17	--		this value MUST be set via signal declaration!
